Name: Justine Bennett
universityAnswer: Final Year Electrical Engineering/Finance at QUT
whyStudyAnswer: I decided to study engineering because it combines two of my favorite things; maths and creativity. As engineers we get to dream up some of the coolest gadgets and actually have the skill set to make them a reality!
whyRobogalsAnswer: I was dragged into Robogals by a friend and stayed for the wholesome atmosphere and fun opportunities. I also really enjoy the workshops and love to see how excited the students get when they successfully code a robot for the first time.
appliedStemAnswer: Pumped hydro storage, the internet, self driving cars, self watering plants...the list goes on!
